-- Iron-Ore Pricing Changes Cause Smaller Shipments for Mills, Baosteel Says
-- B y   W i n g - G a r   C h e n g
-- 2010-11-10T02:58:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-10/iron-ore-pricing-changes-cause-smaller-shipments-for-mills-baosteel-says.html
The introduction of quarterly
pricing for iron ore is causing steelmakers to organize smaller
shipments, Dai Zhihao, vice president at Baosteel Group Corp.,
said today at a conference in Guangzhou, China.  To contact the reporter on this story:
